Name: Astrofall
About the game: [[ //TEXT TRANSMISSION// ]] ASTROFALL Can You Survive the Astrofall? ONLY ONE WILL MAKE IT... Astrofall is a online multiplayer survival platformer, where players compete to make it to the rescue shuttle first to win. Created to be a fast and fun multiplayer experience, Astrofall is perfect to load up for a quick session to test your reflexes against friends and foes. Inspired by the likes of “Mirrors Edge” and 'Fall Guys' Astrofall looks to fill a gap in-between casual competitive fun set in real world settings. Providing yet another light-hearted thrill to the finish line. The perfect way to competivly settle a score, in-game.
